---
title: Chimichurri Burgers with Avocado, Monterey Jack and Cabbage Slaw
description: Chimichurri—an Argentine herb sauce—is one of the most flavourful condiments out there. We’re making it with parsley, cilantro, lemon, and garlic for a kick. Its brightness perfectly cuts through the burger’s intense richness.
